title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 14 2022
description:
Donald Trump Jr. joins Clay and Buck to talk about the blockbuster revelation that Hillary Clinton's campaign spied on the Trump campaign and the Trump White House. Former DNI Ratcliffe: Expect many more Durham indictments. C&B bring us up to speed on the breaking news in the Ukraine situation, CNN reports Putin will invade on January 16th.
